abstracts.cdata!:
The project consists of: improvement and
            subsequent maintenance of about 1,000 km of feeder roads and
            maintenance of about 250 km of existing feeder roads;
            purchase of highway equipment and spare parts and of
            materials and supplies for project operations; technical
            assistance for project implementation and monitoring;
            construction of a headquarters building for BPP.
